{
  "stem": "12462.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the only conversation I ever had with Goering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] What happened to Goering?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Goering, of course, was sentenced to death by hanging.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was executed after the appeal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was executed in that manner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think, 10 of the 22 who were tried were actually executed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Goering committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] Of the conspiracy charge to wage aggressive war, crimes against-- war crimes and crimes against humanity, of various kinds.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the head of the Air Force, the head of the Ministry of Aviation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the designated successor to Hitler, number one, appointed just after the war started, in case Hitler died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Hess was designated as the number two defendant to succeed, the number two official to succeed Hitler or Goering, in case both of them died.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hess was the-- was appointed by Hitler to be the head of the Nazi party underneath Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was made a Reich minister without portfolio in the government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had the right to pass notes and make memoranda on any proposals that his deputies brought to him, which were-- were proposals of Reich ministers or other people.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he kind of had a-- a-- the way of being a veto man underneath Hitler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't exercise that very heavily, as far as we could determine, or as far as I remember.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he became constantly less important in the Nazi regime as time went along, because other people were put into higher positions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put-- the role of the party was exercised through other means, as well as the-- the role of the Nazi state.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was found guilty of conspiracy and found guilty of-- of war crimes and crimes against humanity, up to that time when he flew to Scotland in 1941.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
